@META
dir: skillsPraut/src/templates/
updated: 2026-04-09
files: 10
stack: React, Remotion, TypeScript, @remotion/transitions

@EXPORTS
CaseStudyTemplate.tsx: CaseStudyTemplate — Problem → Solution → Implementation → Results
ComparisonTemplate.tsx: ComparisonTemplate — A vs B side-by-side + recommendation
DeepDiveTemplate.tsx: DeepDiveTemplate — Hook → 5 chapters → Outro
ExplainerTemplate.tsx: ExplainerTemplate — Hook → Definition + Example → Takeaway → Outro
MythBustingTemplate.tsx: MythBustingTemplate — Hook → Myth vs Reality → Evidence → Conclusion
NewsTemplate.tsx: NewsTemplate — Headline → Context → Details → Impact → Opinion → Outro
ReviewTemplate.tsx: ReviewTemplate — Hook → Demo → Pros/Cons → Verdict
ShortTemplate.tsx: ShortTemplate — 9:16 Hook → Punchline → CTA (60s)
TopTenTemplate.tsx: TopTenTemplate — Hook → countdown #10→#1 → Outro
TutorialTemplate.tsx: TutorialTemplate — Hook → Heading → Steps → Outro

@PROCESSES
video-flow: Hook (HookCard 90f) → TransitionSeries (fade) → content slides → EndScreen

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: components/frame/* | components/chapters/* | components/cards/* | components/lists/* | components/typography/* | components/cta/* | components/educational/* | styles/tokens
external: @remotion/transitions (TransitionSeries, linearTiming, fade, slide)

@STANDARDS
- ALL templates use PrautVideoFrame (or PrautShortFrame for ShortTemplate)
- ALL transitions use fade() with timing.medium (24f)
- ShortTemplate uses slide() transition instead of fade
- Hook phase: 90 frames (3s)
- Chapter intro: 60 frames (2s)
- EndScreen: 120 frames (4s)
- All templates are fade-transitioned via TransitionSeries
